params.name: data.name
params.description: Required. The name of the Model resource. Format: projects/{project}/locations/{location}/models/{model} In order to retrieve a specific version of the model, also provide the version ID or version alias. Example: projects/{project}/locations/{location}/models/{model}@2 or projects/{project}/locations/{location}/models/{model}@golden If no version ID or alias is specified, the "default" version will be returned. The "default" version alias is created for the first version of the model, and can be moved to other versions later on. There will be exactly one default version.
